    "It also raises questions about the generalizability and adaptability of the models to diverse educational settings and learner needs.",
    "Overcoming these challenges requires not only innovative approaches to data collection and sharing in the educational domain, but also the employment of methods for data augmentation and generation [107][108][109].Consistency and ethics: Studies on Architecture-Centric Software Engineering (ACSE) using ChatGPT highlight several concerns [66].",
